    "Name": "Aeron VTOL",
    "Details": "The Aeron attack VTOL (Bombast) was derived from prototypes created by the Word of Blake at the beginning of the Jihad era. These experimental models mounted a new vector thrust propulsion system on a Hawk Moth chassis. The Aeron carries a single Bombast Laser mounted in the nose. This weapon is aimed with the assistance of a battle-grade Targeting Computer. This allows the VTOL to target enemy units quickly and accurately even while moving at high speed. \n\n<b><color=#ffcc00>Biome Restrictions: This unit can not deploy in Lunar biomes.</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#ffcc00>Movement: 12/18 hexes / 360/540 meters.</color></b>\n\n<color=#ffcc00><b>Armor:</b> Heavy Ferro-Fibrous\n<b>Structure:</b> Structure\n<b>Values       A        S  </b>\n<b>Front</b>       115     15\n<b>Left</b>          85     15\n<b>Right</b>        85     15\n<b>Rear</b>         75     15\n\n<b>Total</b>      375     75</color>\n\n<color=#ff0000>Quirk: Accurate Weapon - Laser</color>",
